criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Be a military service member seeking surf or hike therapy as part of the Wounded, Ill,
             and Injured Wellness program at Naval Medical Center San Diego;

          -  Have medical clearance to participate in these programs;

          -  Have a current diagnosis of Major Depressive Disorder based on DSM-5 criteria.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Service members who are currently receiving surf or hike therapy (i.e., have already
             started attending program sessions);

          -  Service members who are currently pregnant
